    • Method Detail

      • getSource

        InputStreamPosition getSource()
        Returns:
        A pointer to where the definition of this object starts (in some input stream). May be null, which indicates that this object was not parsed from some string supplied by the user.

      • setSource

        void setSource(InputStreamPosition pos)
        Sets the location of this object's definition in the stream it was defined in. Intended use is only from within GOALParser.
        Parameters:
        pos - The location.
